text: The Wild Dog Dingo () is a 1962 Soviet drama movie directed by Yuli Karasik.Министр культуры поздравил коллектив "Ленфильма" с юбилеем киностудииДИКАЯ СОБАКА ДИНГО It stars Galina Polskikh, Vladimir Osobik, and Talas Umurzakov. == Actors == * Galina Polskikh as Tanya * Vladimir Osobik as Kolya * Talas Umurzakov as Filka * Anna Rodionova as Zhenya * Inna Kondrateva as Mother * Nikolai Timofeyev as Father == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1962 movies Category:Soviet drama movies
title: The Wild Dog Dingo
